{"id":"aecdb0ca-e7bb-4889-adc2-aee5328e11f2","name":"🐾 Mewgenics' Class Mini-Bosses ☢️","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 59, 59);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 235, 235); color: inherit;\">\"Well... you take a cat and rub it on a cat then that cat gets all fat! Not too sure what's up with that... Meeewwwwgenics!\"</mark></em></strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/IJMPs2vHYw9PLILp1qsqY.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(195, 115, 242); color: inherit;\">All of the initial messages assume you are an anthropomorphic cat with the exception of the CYoS message. Sorry, persona users.</mark></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(195, 115, 242); color: inherit;\">(This bot will be continuously updated until I think I've basically added everything necessary.)</mark></em></strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Awesome bot I suddenly got the idea for on a random Tuesday right after I got Mewgenics as one of my recent obsessions. May or may not be the biggest bot I'll make.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Go play/buy the game <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/686060/Mewgenics/\" target=\"_blank\">here.</a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Basic rundown of the characters with some of my headcanons and other people's headcanons. (spoilers for the game ahead if you want to experience it first)</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⬇️</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Act 1: The Alley</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/OrvOdzR9jn3QQs4poASza.webp\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Magnus, the Fighter (✅)</mark></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">(art by Discommunicator on Tumblr)</mark></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Du6I4ek3_i-XKtuSj6tu2.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br>Your run-of-the-mill tough guy who enjoys a good fight, though is a tad bit too aggressive. Great guy if you get to know him though.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(21, 161, 0); color: inherit;\">Fenrir, the Hunter (✅)</mark></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(21, 161, 0); color: inherit;\">(same artist as before)</mark></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/QE6MKPmZjQQHcFq4l19bU.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br>Grizzled old man who specializes in guerrilla warfare and hunting. Likes being left alone and dislikes company.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(156, 204, 0); color: inherit;\">Maisie, the Tank (✅)</mark></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(156, 204, 0); color: inherit;\">(same as before)</mark></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/FLubyarYUy4fFThCY_d1F.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br>A tired mother who became a protector out of necessity in order to let her children live a happy life.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 7, 255); color: inherit;\">Lucy, the Mage (✅)</mark></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 7, 255); color: inherit;\">(you get it at this point)</mark></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6q4oItljw","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"Qj1_qXqPr7qvv-_1dg1ta.webp","creator":"LamontTheFirst","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["🎮 Game","🦄 Non-human","👭 Multiple","🎲 RPG","🐺 Furry"],"chats":2036,"messages":68725,"created_at":"2026-03-18T14:03:56.990875+00:00"}